webpackJsonp([54844114396560],{6801:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{post:{html:'<p>Well, not really. But <a title="Davids Medienkritik" href="http://medienkritik.typepad.com/blog/">Davids Medienkritik</a> did just post a <a title="Davids Medienkritik: We Need Your Help!" href="http://medienkritik.typepad.com/blog/2004/05/we_need_your_he.html">plea to help translate</a> posts into English, and I\'ll be helping out now and again (once a week or so). </p>\n<p>Why, espcially considering that David\'s views are, um, somewhat to the right of mine? Because it\'s a good blog, and it starts good conversations. Even if Germans and Americans tend to disagree, at Medienkritik they\'re at least talking to one another. As a bilingual expat, one thing I can offer to the community is to translate things that are interesting, and David\'s points are always interesting and worth considering. </p>\n<p>Translation is hard work and I am by no means a profressional translator, but at least the <a title="Davids Medienkritik: Bush\'s Down ... Oops, He\'s Up! / Bush sinkt ... Hoppla, er steigt!" href="http://medienkritik.typepad.com/blog/2004/05/bushs_down_oops.html">first post</a> was fun. I felt like I was behind enemy lines, writing headlines for the <em>Bild-Zeiting</em>.</p>',fields:{title:"I'm now a Medienkritiker",date:"12 May 2004",url:"https://papascott.de/2004-05-12-im-now-a-medienkritiker/"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/2004-05-12-im-now-a-medienkritiker/",prev:{fields:{title:"Phil Ringnalda",date:"11 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-11-phil-ringnalda/"}},next:{fields:{title:"Living in Europe: Czechia or Czech Republic?",date:"12 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-12-living-in-europe-czechia-or-czech-republic/"}}}}}});
//# sourceMappingURL=path---2004-05-12-im-now-a-medienkritiker-e60429aeca2ec79338e1.js.map